metatags.og:description:
TRAY | 730 followers on LinkedIn | Self-Service Point of Sale | TRAY® is a complete point of sale system for the enterprise that specializes in self-service ordering. We’re changing the way people order and pay in hospitality venues such as entertainment centers, hotels, restaurants, and more.

As a growing number of companies seek to introduce self-service into their operations to improve their customer experience and reduce operating costs, TRAY is the only enterprise-class system that offers a full turnkey solution, as well as a platform solution that can integrate with existing legacy point of sale systems, including Micros and Infogenesis.
